<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="14Aug1937"><font color="red">14 August 1937</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): We are leaving this p.m. for Rheinfelden &hellip; and a p.c. to C. P. Curran. to whom I have not now time to write another long letter saying I forgot The Soldier&apos;s Song (words and music), i.e., the new National Anthem. </div>
